1 available for general governmental expenses.
2 “(3) All premium taxes received by the director pursuant to ORS 731.820
3 shall be paid by the director to the State Treasurer for deposit in the State
4 Fire Marshal Fund.
5 “(4) Assessments received by the department under sections 3 and 5,
6 chapter 538, Oregon Laws 2017, and penalties received by the department
7 under section 6, chapter 538, Oregon Laws 2017, shall be paid into the State
8 Treasury and credited to the Health System Fund established under section
9 2, chapter 538, Oregon Laws 2017.
